title: Thai Pork Stir-Fry with Green Beans, Red Pepper, and Mint
description: Don’t let the pungent aroma of ginger discourage you. It adds a peppery and slightly sweet flavor to a wide variety of Asian dishes. For this quick and easy stir-fry, our chefs put their own spin on a traditional Thai dish called Pad Krapow Moo by pairing ginger and mint.
